<plot>The legend of Sight Tahmineh Milani's strikingly feminist film draws on the literature of Azarbayejan province. The protagonist is a woman novelist who experiences the lives of four women from different social strata. The film offers a fascinating portrait of a range of Iranian women and their problems. Farsi with English subtitle.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?025009</url></doc>
